<h1 id="hey-im-charlie">Hey, I’m Charlie</h1>

<p>I’m an Enterprise Cloud Architect specializing in <strong>Linux</strong>, <strong>Docker</strong>, <strong>Kubernetes</strong>, <strong>SaaS</strong>, <strong>PaaS</strong> and <strong>IaaS</strong> consulting.</p>

<p>I’ve worked with <strong>Docker</strong> since it’s early days and I actively contribute to <a href="https://github.com/kubernetes/kompose/commits?author=cdrage">multiple</a> <a href="https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/commits?author=cdrage">Kubernetes</a> <a href="https://github.com/kedgeproject/kedge/commits?author=cdrage">related</a> projects, including <a href="https://github.com/moby/moby/commits?author=cdrage">Docker</a> <a href="https://github.com/docker/cli/commits?author=cdrage">projects</a>.</p>

<p>I work at <a href="https://redhat.com">Red Hat</a>. I’ve also worked at tech-related companies such as <a href="http://www.fibernetics.ca/about-us/fibernetics-ventures/">Fibernetics Ventures</a> and researched software at <a href="https://uoit.ca/">UOIT</a>.</p>

<p>My consulting services are based out of Waterloo, Ontario, Canada but I do remote freelance work for clients elsewhere. Visit my <a href="/contact">contact</a> information to get a hold of me.</p>
